//! Multi-method trait collision fixture (module B). Exports a DISTINCT trait
//! that shares the bare name `Proc` with `hew::multitrait` but whose `close`
//! returns a plain `i64` instead of a `Result`, and which declares only the one
//! method. An impl that resolves to module A's `Proc` but supplies THIS module's
//! `i64` `close` signature must be REJECTED; the bare `Proc::close` key collides,
//! so conformance must key off the resolved trait's owner-qualified identity.

/// A single-method process trait whose `close` returns a bare status code.
pub trait Proc {
    fn close(val: Self) -> i64;
}
